                    </table>
                    <specpara>
                        <note>
                            <para>Engines equipped with a by-pass filtering system require additional oil.</para>
                        </note>
                    </specpara>
                    <specpara>
                        <note>
                            <para>Order oil leak detector SE-1632 from:</para>
                            <para>Federal Mogul Service Co.</para>
